{"tid":454431,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone x 回收價出左","createTime":"2017-11-01T06:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T07:18:46.000Z","uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbf7d26cb6b2fb97dca74f3889e802d65e3a7ac","tid":454431,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"iPhone X 後日正式開售，「公司貨」未有像 iPhone 8 般提早 1 星期開盤，今日終於有盤口開出。有「公司」向先達收機舖報價，炒價似乎比先前預期再低！<br />\n<br />\n消息人士向 <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6i7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=74eefbe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者透露，「公司貨」價<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 64GB 報 HK$12,800，256GB 部 HK$13,800</span></strong>，暫時兩色同價，11 月 3 日可以交貨，價格未有像預期高，而回收價預計再比此價低 HK$500 至 HK$1,000。不過，去年 iPhone 7 Plus JetBlack 256GB 版，「公司貨」價起初也報 HK$15,000，但於開售第 2 日，「公司貨」缺貨，先達回收價升到 HK$20,000 港元，故此也視乎大陸、外地需求是否強勁<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1937413/iPhone%20X%20%E5%BE%8C%E9%96%80%E8%B2%A8%E5%83%B9%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%20%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%83%B9%E5%BF%85%E5%86%8D%E8%AA%BF%E4%BD%8E%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1937413%2FiPhone%2520X%2520%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%2520%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%25BF%2585%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E4%25BD%258E%25EF%25BC%2581&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6i7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ebd8e280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1937413/iPhone%20X%20%E5%BE%8C%E9%96%80%E8%B2%A8%E5%83%B9%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%20%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%83%B9%E5%BF%85%E5%86%8D%E8%AA%BF%E4%BD%8E%EF%BC%81</a>"},{"pid":"9a644893b80c6fedee448946c5548e9ffd3f6e89","tid":454431,"uid":6026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"SH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.